Your flight includes regional specialties from our country's
rich bounty. During Autumn, the abundance of our
land is reflected everywhere! As winter approaches the
harvest continues, moving to our southerly boundries.
TWA is pleased to pay tribute to the diversity and richness
of American cuisine.
ST. LOUIS
St. Louis is the heartland of the
United States ... TWA offers
convenient service to St. Louis from
major cities throughout the U.S.A.
TO START
TROPICAL HORS D'OEUVRE
Seafood Salad, Papaya Wedge, Lychee with Macadamia Nut
Cream, Cheese Ramekin and Crackers, Ripe Olive.
SALAD
CALIFORNIA ORANGE
Garden Greens with Sliced Orange and
Toasted Almonds ... Poppy Seed Dressing.
ENTREE SELECTIONS
FILET MIGNON
Tenderloin Steak with Oriental Mushroom Sauce,
Parisienne Potatoes and Broccoli.
Sauteed in Lemon Butter with Macadamia Nuts ...
Green Beans and Rice with Chopped Tomato.
CHICKEN CACCIATORE
Baked Chicken in a hearty Sauce
with Tomatoes, Onions and Spices.
Rigatoni Parmesan and Green Peas.
Please accept our apologies if due to previous passenger
selections, your entree preference is not available.
DESSERT
BEL PAESE CHEESE
GHIRARDELLI CHOCOLATE
* HAWAIIAN HAUPIA COCONUT CAKE
INTERNATIONAL COFFEES
ISLAND with Rum
MILANO with Amaretto di Saronno
ROYALE with Remy Martin V.S.O.P. CAROLANS IRISH
TENNESSEE with Jack Daniels
PRIOR TO ARRIVAL
Orange Juice or Guava Nectar
Island Fruit Cup
Coconut Muffin
Cheese Danish
